: 246.74, "end": 247.74, "text": " This is the brass tacks.", "tokens": [51520, 639, 307, 264, 26257, 256, 7424, 13, 51570], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12852076121738978, "compression_ratio": 1.7552447552447552, "no_speech_prob": 0.19067861139774323}, {"id": 64, "seek": 22362, "start": 247.74, "end": 251.3, "text": " There's absolutely nothing else that you need to know about it, I promise you.", "tokens": [51570, 821, 311, 3122, 1825, 1646, 300, 291, 643, 281, 458, 466, 309, 11, 286, 6228, 291, 13, 51748], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12852076121738978, "compression_ratio": 1.7552447552447552, "no_speech_prob": 0.19067861139774323}, {"id": 65, "seek": 25130, "start": 251.3, "end": 255.02, "text": " If they add anything to it, it's just because they want to sound and look different.", "tokens": [50364, 759, 436, 909, 1340, 281, 309, 11, 309, 311, 445, 570, 436, 528, 281, 1626, 293, 574, 819, 13, 50550], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17470556316953717, "compression_ratio": 1.457142857142857, "no_speech_prob": 0.12311996519565582}, {"id": 66, "seek": 25130, "start": 255.02, "end": 261.7, "text": " But this is the algorithmic perspective of a market structure shift intraday.", "tokens": [50550, 583, 341, 307, 264, 9284, 299, 4585, 295, 257, 2142, 3877, 5513, 560, 6206, 320, 13, 50884], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17470556316953717, "compression_ratio": 1.457142857142857, "no_speech_prob": 0.12311996519565582}, {"id": 67, "seek": 25130, "start": 261.7, "end": 268.42, "text": " Now keep this price level in mind, so it's essentially $14,600 and $14,820.", "tokens": [50884, 823, 1066, 341, 3218, 1496, 294, 1575, 11, 370, 309, 311, 4476, 1848, 7271, 11, 15707, 293, 1848, 7271, 11, 23, 2009, 13, 51220], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17470556316953717, "compression_ratio": 1.457142857142857, "no_speech_prob": 0.12311996519565582}, {"id": 68, "seek": 25130, "start": 268.42, "end": 272.54, "text": " We're just eyeballing it, OK?", "